352
00:45:13,272 --> 00:45:15,137
See you later.

353
00:45:20,479 --> 00:45:24,006
See? You can do it if you try!

354
00:45:24,383 --> 00:45:26,749
Just keep on like that.

355
00:45:28,087 --> 00:45:29,952
Go and get ready!

356
00:45:36,062 --> 00:45:37,427
