when there is something...

526
01:08:43,087 --> 01:08:44,782
That's called 'style'.

527
01:08:46,056 --> 01:08:47,421
I see.

528
01:08:49,093 --> 01:08:55,931
Perhaps this money will buy you
kimonos to fill that chest of drawers.

529
